    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it really shows in every little detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for all your upcoming adventures, this is definitely the one. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
